Executive Profile
John R. Loyack  Director, AMCON Distributing CompanyAgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 7 different industries.See Board Relationships54$60,000
Background

		Mr. John R. Loyack served as the Chief Executive Officer and President at Optim Energy, LLC. Mr. Loyack was the President of Compression Polymers Holding II Corp., since February 10, 2006 and Chief Operating Officer since September 2005. Mr. Loyack served as Chief Executive Officer of Cpcapitol Acquisition Corp. since January 1, 2007 and also served as Chief Executive Officer of EnergyCo, LLC. He joined Compression Polymers Holding II Corp., in September 2005 as Chief ... Financial Officer. Mr. Loyack served as the President of Santana Products, Inc. and served as its Chief Operating Officer since February 10, 2006. He served as Chief Operating Officer and Treasurer of AZEK Building Products, Inc. and served as its President. He served as President of Cpcapitol Acquisition Corp. from February 10, 2006 to December31, 2006 and also served as its Chief Operating Officer until December31, 2006. He served as Chief Executive Officer of Santana Products, Inc. Mr. Loyack served as Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of Public Service Co. of New Mexico since January 1, 2003. Mr. Loyack served as Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of PNM Resources Inc. from January 1, 2003 to August 9, 2005 and September 1, 2005 respectively. He served as President and Chief Executive Officer of CPG International I Inc. and served as President of Scranton Products Inc. from January 1, 2007 to October 3, 2007. He served as Chief Executive Officer of CPG International, Inc. from Janaury 1, 2007 to October 3, 2007, President from February 10, 2006 to December 31, 2006 and Chief Operating Officer from September 2005 to December 31, 2006. He served as Chief Accounting Officer, Vice President and Controller of PNM Resources Inc. from 1999 to 2002. Prior to his position at PNM Resources, he served as Senior Manager, Business Analysis Union Pacific Corporation since January 1, 1996. He served as Director of Financial Reporting of Union Pacific Corporation from October 1, 1998 to July 19, 1999. He has been a Director of AMCON Distributing Company since September 2003, Cpcapitol Acquisition Corp. Since January 1, 2007. He has been a Director of CPG International I Inc. since January 1, 2007. He serves as Director of AZEK Building Products, Inc. Mr. Loyack serves as a Director of Santana Products, Inc. and as a Director of CREAC One. He served as Director of CPG International, Inc. from Janaury 1, 2007 to October 3, 2007. Earlier in his career, Mr. Loyack held positions with Lutron Electronics and PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP. Mr. Loyack is a Certified Public Accountant. Mr. Loyack received a B.S. in accounting from King's College and an M.B.A. from Lehigh University.Read Full Background




