Insider Activity


Individual




John R. Loyack



Mr. John R. Loyack is Independent Director at AMCON Distributing Co., President & Chief Executive Officer at CPC Sub I Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer at CPH Sub I Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer at Compression Polymers Holding Corp., and CFO, Treasurer & Vice President-Business Affairs at King's College (Pennsylvania). He is on the Board of Directors at AMCON Distributing Co.
Mr. Loyack was previously employed as President & Chief Executive Officer by Optim Energy LLC, President by Scranton Products, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by CPG International I, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer by CPG International LLC, Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by PNM Resources, Inc., and President & Chief Executive Officer by Azek Building Products, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from King's College (Pennsylvania) and an MBA from Lehigh University.



